  "response": "The processing time for an iStockphoto photography contributor application can vary, but it typically takes anywhere from a few days to a couple of weeks. The review process depends on several factors, including the volume of applications being processed and the completeness of the submitted materials. If you haven't heard back within a reasonable time frame, it's a good idea to check your email (including the spam folder) or reach out to iStock support for an update on your application.",
